706087f-a.title: Brooklyn: Nostrand Avenue - Macon Street
706087f-a.text:
ostrand Avenue, east side, between Macon and Halsey Streets,
looking porth and showing the Cirls' High School.
P. L. Spe rr
August 26, 1941
2. Nostrand Ave., north across Fulton St., B'klyn.
May 1, 1942
P.L. Sperr, photographer
